 ires\, enhance physical body awareness\, practice the art of detachme
 nt and cultivate a state of inner peace. Mindful movement is a series
  of yoga postures that incorporates mindful body awareness to cultiva
 te unity of the body\, mind and Spirit. \n* Suitable for all Levels o
 f Fitness Intensity Rating                   \n\nPlease sign up on th
 e Village App.
