SUMMARY:OV Coached Pickleball (60m)
DESCRIPTION:Room: OV Pickle East 1\, 2\nLocation: Ocotillo Village\nPi
 ckleball Coaching is now at the Ocotillo Village every Sunday. Open t
 o all player levels who are needing or wanting some extra coaching\, 
 to sharpen there game play.\n\nSunday Group Coached Sessions will run
  $30pp from 10-11am\n\nFollowed by Free Open play for anyone 11am to 
 1pm\n\nRegular Open Play will also continue on week days on Tuesday a
 nd Thursday's\, Alternating each week from 1:00PM Noon to 3:00PM. \n\
 n3 Courts will be available on the Basketball Court. The Basketball C
 ourt will not be open for for Basketball play until after 1pm on Sund
 ays and after 3pm on Tuesdays and Thursdays.\n\nCourt rotation is ava
 ilable based on first come\, first serve basis. Rules and Play Policy
  will be posted at the Court.\n\n*There will be no Officials. Honesty
  and Good Sportsmanship will be expected at all times.
END:VEVENT
